query:
SELECT
                tl.id as "id!: Uuid",
                tl.project_id as "project_id!: Uuid",
                tl.name,
                tl.color,
                tl.position as "position!: i32",
                tl.created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
            FROM task_labels tl
            INNER JOIN task_label_assignments tla ON tla.label_id = tl.id
            WHERE tla.task_id = $1
            ORDER BY tl.position ASC, tl.name ASC
